          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="detailed-guidelines" class="doc-section-title">Complete Do's and Don'ts</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Guidelines for effective sidebar navigation usage.</p>
            <div class="do-dont-grid">
              <div class="do-card"><span class="card-label">Do</span><ul>
                <li><strong>Reflect current page:</strong> Always set exactly one item to <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Active</code> to reflect the current page.</li>
                <li><strong>Add state purpose:</strong> Use the <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Add</code> state only for primary creation actions (e.g. "Add Config").</li>
                <li><strong>User-driven collapse:</strong> Use <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Icon Only</code> only as the collapsed state, toggled by the user.</li>
                <li><strong>Tooltips in collapsed:</strong> Show tooltips on all items when in <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Icon Only</code> mode.</li>
                <li><strong>Preserve set items:</strong> Keep all items from the product's defined set &#8212; disable rather than hide items users shouldn't access.</li>
              </ul></div>
              <div class="dont-card"><span class="card-label">Don't</span><ul>
                <li><strong>Missing location:</strong> Leave all items in <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Default</code> &#8212; users need a clear location indicator.</li>
                <li><strong>Misuse Add:</strong> Use <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Add</code> state for regular navigation destinations.</li>
                <li><strong>Default collapsed:</strong> Default to <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Icon Only</code> &#8212; expanded labels aid discoverability.</li>
                <li><strong>Missing tooltips:</strong> Hide labels in collapsed mode without providing a hover tooltip.</li>
                <li><strong>Remove restricted items:</strong> Remove items from the nav for items that are merely restricted &#8212; use <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Disabled</code> state with a tooltip explaining why.</li>
              </ul></div>
            </div>
